Much known as "bomber", they're a type of combat aircraft design to attack ground and sea targets by dropping air-to-ground weaponry such as firing torpedoes or bombs. Hence the name.

In Kancolle, they can be put in a [[Land Base Aerial Support|Land Base]] and does bonus damage against Installation-type Abyssal Foes. However they required to be escorted by fighters.